lyTime":"2016-12-16T07:23:20.000Z","msg":"五年前接觸攝影無耐，<br />\n同朋友拎住本叫藍色聖經嘅書就出發去希臘同土耳其<br />\n用手機懶得搵電腦原相，Facebook抄返D相落黎分享下<br />\n<br />\n希臘聖托里尼海景<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34729mr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34729mr.jpg&h=82c126b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n土耳其伊斯坦堡地下水庫<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/151733_eb9d84b29259d5d633c5a9ab935ffdf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F151733_eb9d84b29259d5d633c5a9ab935ffdf4.jpg&h=af0d81a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n土耳其伊斯坦堡某日一條大街，覺得好特別所以影低左<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/151806_4b733d590822cb45e0fea3d00d967a09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F151806_4b733d590822cb45e0fea3d00d967a09.jpg&h=5a0172cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說伊斯坦堡好多靚貓，比貓奴們J下<br />\n(一樣懶得搵原相所以粗糙地遮下Logo免自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/152030_0fd631f29b46923a17f69d8da976459d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F152030_0fd631f29b46923a17f69d8da976459d.jpg&h=0d564c80&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qY082vw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqY082vw.jpg&h=636b37fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D18qq5O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD18qq5O.jpg&h=775d8e2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdQ0xXp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkdQ0xXp.jpg&h=57e15a39&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/152031_b8683a59d3141732f988c248879823b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F152031_b8683a59d3141732f988c248879823b2.jpg&h=d83f1380&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/152044_cbb3559e150e57ddce5e53e4bfa0db9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F152044_cbb3559e150e57ddce5e53e4bfa0db9c.jpg&h=fe993c27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/152044_baf2111c5ae3d93ea2a9b39505c45dbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F152044_baf2111c5ae3d93ea2a9b39505c45dbe.jpg&h=c1c4aeb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當地人對街貓好友善，餐廳都係由得佢地入黎瞓，<br />\n連掃地嘅叔叔都隨身帶住貓糧餵貓，<br />\n所以當地貓好親近人任你影<br />\n<br />\n其實有另外一張我等船走去餵貓比貓圍...<br />\n不過廢事比人話收兵就唔分享啦，上面貓圖夠晒J <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce30e0b4f4c2c48a30fbebcc43eca780b00a176","tid":41772,"uid":53416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:26:00.000Z","msg":"6. Nanaimo Harbour, Nanaimo, BC, Canada<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/n31x6bja\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fn31x6bja&h=ede819f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7faa6adb97aab6289543a8f60631b415dbb1246e","tid":41772,"uid":53416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:29:20.000Z","msg":"7. Sunset Boulevard, Los Angeles, CA, USA<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9zekpon8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9zekpon8&h=db886efe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d919ea4610c26aec16d3bd9a165774786e661ae","tid":41772,"uid":53416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:32:56.000Z","msg":"8. Treasure Island, San Francisco, CA, USA<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kp9ofhb1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkp9ofhb1&h=5da71d8d&s={SIZE}\" />